{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_MM04_ST3_610.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0xd,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, maybe this place'll have what I'm looking for..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x185,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "You said something like that before...<CR>I didn't ask, since I thought it might<CR>be something personal..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x186,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "But, what is it that you're looking for, Ayesha?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Well, it's a flower. A certain flower that only blooms once every 100 years in a plain."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Oh, but if that plain has become a wasteland, then maybe the flower withered and died as well..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x187,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Oh, hold on! I'm not sure if it's once in a hundred years, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I've heard a story about a flower that's always been a bud!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "And, it's not too far from here.<CR>Would you like to go see it?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Yes, I'd love to go!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Okay! Then I'm gonna go back home and let them know where we're going."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "After that, I'll meet up with you near the flower. So, the bud is located..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I have a good idea of where it is. I don't think I'll get lost."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xf,
            "name_id": 0xf,
            "extra_id": 0x19f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Okay, then I'll see you later!<CR>Buh-bye for now!"
        }
    ]
}